channel.title: Great site for you web developers who want $$$!
channel.description:
http://marketplace.sitepoint.com/ You don't gotta believe but there is a premium site that costed $25, 000! It was simpple but man was it fucking crazy dude, that like make website development stupid & useless. So I'm not gonna just talk about it, imma gonna refer you to the proof:
http://marketplace.sitepoint.com/auctions/33130
Pretty good if you askin me :rolleyes:. I haven't actually sold anything since my paypal got closed since I was under age though lol, but I sure would do this if I still had my paypal acc - I had money flow like crazy, except only 1 problem I couldn't get cash cuz i didnt have no bank lololol I had to use paypal and buy & sell from computer :mad:.....
